  "texts": [
    "Human perception, reflecting the multimodal structure of our world, is completed by the interaction of information in different modalities such as language, visuals, video, and sound.",
    "Recently, text-based LLMs have been supplemented with other understanding and perception capabilities, leading to the development of multimodal LLMs [25].",
    "Medicine is also inherently multifaceted, and the ability of healthcare professionals to make decisions in clinical settings encompasses multimodal reasoning; therefore, multimodal LLMs are believed to have significant potential in the field of medicine [5].",
    "However, while multimodal LLMs continue to advance in various fields, they require further research due to their limited use, especially in medical and dental research [26].",
    "For this reason, this study utilized multimodal LLMs like Table 1 Questions 1-Can regenerative endodontic treatment be performed on immature teeth with periapical lesions?"
  ]
}